            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Accountability Map with agent roles</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50/50">
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">What I own</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Job description, responsibilities</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Authority boundaries per agent</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Who to ask for help</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Manager, team leads, Slack channels</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Coordination patterns, message bus</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50/50">
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">When to escalate</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Escalation path, chain of command</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Escalation rules, human-in-the-loop gates</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">What tools to use</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">IT provisioning, tool access</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">MCP tools, API keys, service connections</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50/50">
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-900">What went wrong before</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Tribal knowledge, war stories</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Documented failure modes with evidence</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 text-gray-500 text-sm">The difference: a human absorbs context over weeks. An agent needs it all in the first prompt. The OOS delivers it.</p>
  </div>
</section>

